Text: Please help to seed. 43 downloaded and 1 helping to seed. I am not here for the good of my health. The bay is struggling as it is. The leeches in the bay are becoming a real pain in the arse. If this carries on you will have no bay to fish in. Thank you to that 1 kind person who like myself and many other pirates keep the ship afloat. All it takes is a little give and take and the gold will keep emerging. Thanks.
